thread.title_full: CustomUSB reviewed by Luke Parker Photography

author: Luke Parker Photography
title: Luke Parker Photography
text: I had 50 USB drives Lazer engraved by them. They were very easy to work with and gave me a good looking finished product that represents me well to my clients. They even gave me a free size upgrade on the drives I ordered! I'll certainly use them again.
